Source: lua-posix
Section: interpreters
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Enrico Tassi <gareuselesinge@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.1.3), dh-lua (>= 8), libncurses5-dev, lua-bitop
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
